#: contactYourProvider.description
msgid ""
"&brandShortName; can allow you to get to your mail using the provided "
"configurations. However, you should contact your administrator or email "
"provider regarding these improper connections. See the Thunderbird FAQ for "
"more information."
msgstr ""
"Mae &brandShortName; yn gallu caniatáu i chi estyn eich e-bost drwy "
"ddefnyddio'r ffurfweddiad parod. Er hynny, dylech gysylltu â'ch gweinyddwr "
"neu ddarparwr e-bost ynghylch cysylltiadau anaddas. Gw. Cwestiynau "
"Thunderbird am ragor o wybodaeth."

#: insecureServer.tooltip.title
msgid "Warning! This is an insecure server."
msgstr "Rhybudd! Mae hwn yn weinydd anniogel."

